high_descs: Move to the stove across from the refrigerator
Pick up the pan from the stove
Move to the fridge across from the stove
Open the fridge, place the pan inside, close the door, let pan chill for a moment before removing and closing the door again
Move to the stove across from the fridge
Place the pan back on to the stove on the left burner
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan onto the stove

high_descs: Turn right towards the wall and then turn left towards the stove.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the pan on the top rack, close the fridge for it to cool down, and then take the pan out.
Place the pan on the left stove top closest to you.
anns.task_desc: Cool down the pan on the stove.

high_descs: Turn to the fridge on your right, then turn right and walk to the stove.
Pick up the black pan from the fridge.
Turn around, then walk back to the fridge.
Chill the pan in the fridge for a few seconds, then remove it.
Turn around, and walk back over to the stove.
Place the pan on the front left burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pan on a stove.
